      h2 4. 2D Transformations
      
      p You can perform some transormation on objects in order to position or scale them to your liking. I'll show you two of these transformations: rotate and scale.
      
      pre
        code(class="language-css")
          | div{
          |   width: 85px; 
          |   height: 85px; 
          |   background-color: #fbda59;
          |   transform: rotate(45deg) scale(0.5, 0.5);
          | }
      
