      h2 6. Colums
      
      p If you want to create some colums out of one single paragraph, you're in luck. This next option lets you start with one block of text and cuts it into different colums for you:
      
      pre
        code(class="language-css")
          | div{
          |   column-count: 3;
          |   column-gap: 40px;
          |   column-rule: 3px outset #fbda59;
          | }
      
